OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FAs the public inquiry into the
OL,7,FNottingham Attacks finishes hearing
OL,8,Fevidence, we've compiled some of the
OL,9,Fkey pieces of evidence.
OL,11,FEach day of this inquiry, we learned
OL,12,Fmore about the care of triple killer
OL,13,FValdo Calocane, the police
OL,14,Finvestigation into the attacks and the
OL,15,Ftreatment of the victims.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
