CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FCalocane killed students Barnaby
OL,7,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar, both
OL,8,F19, and grandfather Ian Coates, 65,
OL,9,Fbefore trying to murder Wayne Birkett,
OL,10,FSharon Miller and Marcin Gawronski
OL,11,Fwith a van on June 13 2023, in
OL,12,FNottingham, leaving them seriously
OL,13,Finjured.
OL,15,FHe is currently detained indefinitely
OL,16,Fin a high-security hospital after
OL,17,Fprosecutors accepted his not guilty
OL,18,Fpleas to murder, at his sentencing at
OL,19,FNottingham Crown Court in January 2024.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
