OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FThe Nottingham Inquiry started on the
OL,7,F23rd of February and, since then, has
OL,8,Fheard from 164 witnesses over 14
OL,9,Fweeks, as the lead-up to the attacks
OL,10,Fand the aftermath were examined.
OL,12,FWork is now beginning on the report
OL,13,Fahead of a further hearing for closing
OL,14,Fsubmissions on 8th and 9th September.
OL,16,FThe Chair is required to deliver
OL,17,Ffindings and recommendations by May
OL,18,F2027.
OL,20,FThe warning signs: "Perhaps VC (Valdo
OL,21,FCalocane) will end up killing someone"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
