OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FOne of the key questions this inquiry
OL,7,Fis trying to answer is whether the
OL,8,Fattacks could have been prevented.
OL,10,FThe inquiry looked into violent
OL,11,Fincidents in Valdo Calocane's past,
OL,12,Fand spoke to the people who treated
OL,13,Fhim, all to understand why he was able
OL,14,Fto slip through the cracks of both
OL,15,Fhealth services and law enforcement.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
