PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FConsultant psychiatrist Dr Faizal
OL,7,FSeedat treated the killer at Highbury
OL,8,FHospital in Nottinghamshire, where he
OL,9,Fwas detained under mental health laws
OL,10,Fon four occasions between 2020 and
OL,11,F2022.
OL,13,FHe said Valdo Calocane he could kill
OL,14,Fsomeone years before the attacks.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
