OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FCounsel to the Inquiry, Rachel
OL,7,FLangdale KC, asked Dr Seedat about a
OL,8,Fnote which said Calocane had "no
OL,9,Finsight or remorse" about violent
OL,10,Fincidents involving his neighbours,
OL,11,Fincluding one where a woman was
OL,12,Fseverely injured, and "perhaps VC
OL,13,F(Valdo Calocane) will end up killing
OL,14,Fsomeone".
OL,16,FThe inquiry heard that in May 2020,
OL,17,Fthe former mechanical engineering
OL,18,Fstudent kicked repeatedly at a woman's
OL,19,Fdoor while experiencing psychosis,
OL,20,Fcausing her to jump from the first-
OL,21,Ffloor window and break her spine.
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@SO]tD@WOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
