OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FDr Seedat told the inquiry, "I painted
OL,7,Fthe worst case scenario in terms of
OL,8,Fwhat could happen if he continued with
OL,9,Fhis behaviour.
OL,11,F"I reminded him that... next time, if
OL,12,Fyou continue this, that you would end
OL,13,Fup killing someone.
OL,15,F"So it was in that context to try and
OL,16,Fshock or highlight the importance of
OL,17,Fthe implications of his behaviours in
OL,18,Forder to try and help him start to
OL,19,Fdevelop some sort of understanding of
OL,20,Fthe gravity of the situation."
OL,26,@nD@]OUsD@AOUwD@AOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
