OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,F"And it was with that I meant that
OL,7,Fcomment ` not that he would kill
OL,8,Fsomeone physically by his hand."
OL,10,FBut there were multiple other examples
OL,11,Fof Calocane's potential for violence.
OL,13,FA flatmate of Valdo Calocane told the
OL,14,Finquiry how the triple killer put him
OL,15,Fin a headlock and then prevented him
OL,16,Ffrom leaving their shared kitchen when
OL,17,Fthey were both students.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`O]
