OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,F"I got lucky and I'm fine," he said.
OL,8,F"Maybe I wouldn't have, but that's
OL,9,Fwhere we are."
OL,11,FAnother violent outburst happened a
OL,12,Fmonth before the killings.
OL,14,FCalocane began working as an agency
OL,15,Fwarehouse operative for logistics
OL,16,Fcompany Arvato in Derby.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@[O]pD@AOUqD@NO]
