OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FOn May 5 2023, he attacked two members
OL,7,Fof staff, who were a married couple,
OL,8,Fpunching the male colleague in the
OL,9,Fface before pushing over the female
OL,10,Fcolleague and hurting her leg, the
OL,11,Finquiry heard.
OL,13,FGiving evidence on Tuesday, a training
OL,14,Fcoordinator for the company at the
OL,15,Ftime, identified only as Louisa,
OL,16,Freferred to Calocane as 'VC', "We
OL,17,Fheard a scream from the back of the
OL,18,Fwarehouse.
OL,20,F"I then started to move in that
OL,21,Fdirection.
OL,26,@xD@_OU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/57
