OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,F"The two victims ` the wife, she was
OL,7,Fin front of the husband, the husband
OL,8,Fwas already on the floor. He had
OL,9,Falready been assaulted.
OL,11,FAs I got into the area I stood myself
OL,12,Fin front of VC so my back would have
OL,13,Fbeen to the victims.
OL,15,F"VC was just stood in front of me,
OL,16,Fthere was no words coming out of VC's
OL,17,Fmouth.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
