OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,F"What was different is for the seconds
OL,7,FI was stood in front of VC his
OL,8,Fattention was not on me. He was
OL,9,Flooking through me and his attention
OL,10,Fwas on the male victim that was on the
OL,11,Ffloor."
OL,13,FShe said she remembers the male victim
OL,14,Fsaying he had been hit to the side of
OL,15,Fhis face, which had triggered an old
OL,16,Finjury, and that he did not know why
OL,17,Fhe had been attacked.
OL,19,FAn apology from police: "We should
OL,20,Fhave arrested him"
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@GO]
