OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FWithin this long string of violence,
OL,7,Fthere was one incident that kept being
OL,8,Freferred back to through the inquiry,
OL,9,Fbecause it could have led to
OL,10,FCalocane's arrest before the attacks.
OL,12,FTwo years before the Nottingham
OL,13,Fattack, Calocane, while he was still a
OL,14,Fmechanical engineering student at the
OL,15,FUniversity of Nottingham, headbutted,
OL,16,Fpunched and swung handcuffs at a
OL,17,Fpolice officer on September 3, 2021,
OL,18,Fcausing swelling to his face.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
