OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FHealth care services: "You lost him?"
OL,8,FThe quality of medical care Valdo
OL,9,FCalocane received was central to the
OL,10,Finquiry.
OL,12,FCalocane was diagnosed with paranoid
OL,13,Fschizophrenia in 2020, and his mental
OL,14,Fstate was the critical factor in the
OL,15,FCrown Prosecution Service accepting
OL,16,Fhis not guilty plea, and his eventual
OL,17,Fsentence to an indefinite hospital
OL,18,Forder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G20/57
