OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FAs Calocane was in regular contact
OL,7,Fwith mental health services since his
OL,8,Fdiagnosis, what they knew about his
OL,9,Fviolent tendencies and what
OL,10,Finterventions could have been taken,
OL,11,Fwere a key line of questioning through
OL,12,Fthe inquiry.
OL,14,FThe inquiry heard he was discharged
OL,15,Ffrom mental health services to his GP
OL,16,Fjust months before he killed three
OL,17,Fpeople in Nottingham because
OL,18,Fhealthcare workers could not find him.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G21/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37622
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FIn September 2022, Calocane was
OL,7,Fdischarged by the trust's Early
OL,8,FIntervention in Psychosis (EIP)
OL,9,Fservice because he failed to turn up
OL,10,Ffor appointments or make contact with
OL,11,Fthe team.
OL,13,FIt was also revealed that the trust
OL,14,Fdid not tell Nottinghamshire Police
OL,15,Fthat Calocane had been discharged from
OL,16,Fits services.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G22/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37623
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FEmma Robinson, who was a team leader
OL,7,Fat the Nottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust, told the inquiry,
OL,9,Fwhich is looking into events leading
OL,10,Fup to the attacks, on Tuesday, that
OL,11,FCalocane's care co-ordinator, Gary
OL,12,FCarter, had attended his address, made
OL,13,Fcalls to him, and sent a letter that
OL,14,Fwent unanswered.
OL,16,FEmma Robinson speaking at the public
OL,17,Finquiry.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G23/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37624
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FTim Moloney KC, who represents the
OL,7,Ffamilies of Mr Webber, Ms O'Malley-
OL,8,FKumar and Mr Coates, asked, "When you
OL,9,Fdischarged, did you think about the
OL,10,Frisk to the public from this man, who
OL,11,FEIP would not visit alone, would not
OL,12,Fvisit at home unless absolutely
OL,13,Fnecessary?
OL,15,F"Did you consider the risks to the
OL,16,Fpublic from that man?"
OL,26,@pD@]OUwD@AOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G24/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37625
SC,0025
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FShe replied, "We did consider that,
OL,7,Fbut we felt that within the time of
OL,8,Fdecision, we had no holding powers, we
OL,9,Fcouldn't work with him, we couldn't
OL,10,Ffind him at this point. We just
OL,11,Fcouldn't find him to work with him."
OL,13,FThe inquiry heard that Calocane's last
OL,14,Fengagement with the EIP team had been
OL,15,Fby phone on July 16, when he lied
OL,16,Fabout being abroad.
OL,18,FMr Moloney asked, "Had you lost him?"
OL,19,Fto which Ms Robinson replied, "Yes."
OL,26,@nD@NOUsD@dO]zD@SOUzD@eO]{D@_OU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G25/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37626
SC,0026
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FThe lawyer asked, "Is that primarily
OL,7,Fwhy you discharged him?"
OL,9,FMs Robinson said, "Yes, because we
OL,10,Fcouldn't find him to treat him or
OL,11,Fengage him."
OL,13,FA separate medical witness, who hadn't
OL,14,Fpersonally dealt with Valdo Calocane,
OL,15,Fsaid the triple killer should not have
OL,16,Fbeen discharged from mental health
OL,17,Fservices.
OL,26,@nD@SOUoD@XO]qD@SOUsD@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G26/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
