OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37628
SC,0028
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FAnother lawyer for the inquiry, Craig
OL,7,FCarr, asked, "Neither in the discharge
OL,8,Fletter or in any of the correspondence
OL,9,Fyour practice received is there any
OL,10,Fsuggestion that the discharge was
OL,11,Fbased on any assessment of safety,
OL,12,Fsimply that he had disengaged?"
OL,14,F"That's correct," Dr Baker responded.
OL,16,FThe inquiry also sought to determine
OL,17,Fwhether Valdo Calocane was being
OL,18,Fproperly medicated.
OL,26,@oD@NOUtD@_O]vD@AOUvD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G28/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
