PN,37630
SC,0030
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FMr Carter said he felt the handover
OL,7,Fprocess, when he took over as
OL,8,FCalocane's care co-ordinator, was
OL,9,F"inadequate" and agreed that the issue
OL,10,Fof his non-compliance with taking
OL,11,Fmedication, which was mentioned in his
OL,12,Fcare plan as needing ongoing
OL,13,Fmonitoring, was not taken seriously
OL,14,Fenough.
OL,16,FIn a visit to Calocane on 6 November
OL,17,F2020, Mr Carter said he took one
OL,18,Fmonth's worth of medication to him,
OL,19,Fbut Calocane said he still had 10
OL,20,Ftablets left.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G30/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37631
SC,0031
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FMr Carter also visisted Calocane in
OL,7,FAugust 2021 and said he felt Calocane
OL,8,Fwas on the verge of a breakdown and
OL,9,Fconfirmed he was not taking his
OL,10,Fmedication.
OL,12,FVictims failed: "You have tortured
OL,13,Fthese families over and over again."
OL,15,FThe stories of the victims, those who
OL,16,Fwere killed and those who survived,
OL,17,Fwere heard throughout the inquiry.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G31/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
