OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37632
SC,0032
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FWhile their pain, statements and
OL,7,Fstories were all different, one thing
OL,8,Funified them - they believed they'd
OL,9,Fbeen failed by the institutions meant
OL,10,Fto protect them.
OL,12,FEach person affected by the attacks
OL,13,Fhighlighted issues both immediately
OL,14,Fafter the attacks and in the years
OL,15,Fthat followed.
OL,17,FThe families of those killed
OL,18,Frepeatedly returned to what they saw
OL,19,Fas failures of process and
OL,20,Fcommunication from the emergency
OL,21,Fservices.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G32/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
