OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37633
SC,0033
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FIan Coates's family say they found out
OL,7,Fhe had been killed on social media
OL,8,Fbefore they were told by the police.
OL,10,FThe Inquiry also heard that Mr Coates
OL,11,Fhad been left at the crime scene for
OL,12,Fnearly 15 hours while police were
OL,13,Finvestigating.
OL,15,FMr Coates's partner, Elaine Newton,
OL,16,Ftold the public inquiry that she was
OL,17,Ffirst told by police he'd died in a
OL,18,Froad traffic accident.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G33/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
