OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37634
SC,0034
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FShe said, "They said he was in an RTA,
OL,7,Fa road accident. I said 'He will be at
OL,8,Fwork, it's not Ian'. They said 'No,
OL,9,Fit's an RTA'. I said 'Did he crash
OL,10,Finto anyone? What happened?'
OL,12,F"They said 'We can't tell you'. I said
OL,13,F'Is anyone else hurt?' and they said
OL,14,F'We can't tell you'. That's all they
OL,15,Fwere telling me for about five hours."
OL,17,FWhen Elaine Newton eventually found
OL,18,Fout he'd been stabbed, she said it was
OL,19,Flike he'd been "killed twice".
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G34/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
