OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37635
SC,0035
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FPolice later described this as a
OL,7,F"terrible error".
OL,9,FThe conduct of the police was put
OL,10,Funder especially close scrutiny.
OL,12,FThe families of those who died said it
OL,13,Fwas "disgusting" that the teenage
OL,14,Fstabbing victims were tested for drugs
OL,15,Fand alcohol, but their killer was not.
OL,17,FPolice also apologised after officers
OL,18,Faccessed footage from the attacks and
OL,19,Fsent WhatsApp messages about the
OL,20,Fvictims' injuries.
OL,26,@uD@EOUuD@PO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G35/57
