PN,37636
SC,0036
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FEmma Webber, whose 19-year-old son
OL,7,FBarnaby was one of those killed in the
OL,8,Fattack, said a WhatsApp message sent
OL,9,Fby a police officer referencing the
OL,10,Fundergraduate's wounds is "disgusting
OL,11,Fand grotesque".
OL,13,FShe told the inquiry that officers had
OL,14,Fviewed footage of her son "lying on
OL,15,Fthe road, having been brutally stabbed
OL,16,Fmultiple times, fighting for his life
OL,17,Fand ultimately losing it"
OL,26,@rD@[OUsD@NO]vD@[OUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G36/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37637
SC,0037
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FIn her evidence, she repeated the
OL,7,Flanguage used in the messages. They
OL,8,Fdescribed the students as being
OL,9,F"properly butchered" and with "innards
OL,10,Fout".
OL,12,FThe families also took fire at
OL,13,Fmultiple public bodies, including the
OL,14,Fpolice watchdog, the IOPC, and the
OL,15,FCrown Prosecution Service.
OL,17,FDr Sanjoy Kumar described the
OL,18,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,19,F(IOPC) as "nothing but a joke".
OL,26,@{D@KOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G37/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37638
SC,0038
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FMr Kumar said the family went for a
OL,7,Fmeeting with the body with faith in
OL,8,Fthe organisation, but found it
OL,9,F"absurd" when the meeting opened with
OL,10,Fa prayer.
OL,12,FDr Kumar told the inquiry, "The IOPC
OL,13,Fhave been unprofessional and nothing
OL,14,Fbut a joke.
OL,16,F"When people say they are not fit for
OL,17,Fpurpose, I believe that."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@HO]tD@\OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G38/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
