OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37639
SC,0039
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FRachel Watson, the director general of
OL,7,Fthe Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct (IOPC), told the public
OL,9,Finquiry into the attacks that it had
OL,10,F"let down" the families by being "too
OL,11,Fslow" to probe officers' actions.
OL,13,FThe IOPC boss told chairwoman Deborah
OL,14,FTaylor that she hopes that the ongoing
OL,15,Finvestigations into police actions
OL,16,Fwill be concluded by the time the
OL,17,FNottingham Inquiry has finished.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@JO]rD@bOUsD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G39/57
