CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FBut the families weren't satisfied
OL,7,Fwith this.
OL,9,FThey believe a document was "buried"
OL,10,For "covered up" so it would not
OL,11,Fundermine the CPS's decision to accept
OL,12,Fnot guilty pleas to murder.
OL,14,FThat was a report by Nottinghamshire
OL,15,FPolice Detective Constable Neil Beddoe
OL,16,Fin December 2023, which argued that
OL,17,FCalocane had shown "rationality and
OL,18,Funderstanding of consequences".
OL,26,@qD@]OUqD@dO]rD@DOUrD@OO]yD@TOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G43/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
