OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FIt was put into the MG6D folder, which
OL,7,Fis usually used for the most serious
OL,8,Fand sensitive material in criminal
OL,9,Fprosecutions.
OL,11,FThe CPS rejects any suggestion of
OL,12,Fwrongdoing.
OL,14,FThe CPS said DC Beddoe's report was
OL,15,Fprepared to assist the prosecution
OL,16,Fwith submissions as to the appropriate
OL,17,Fsentence and was not considered an
OL,18,Falternative expert opinion to those of
OL,19,Fthe psychiatrists.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G44/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
