CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FIn his evidence to the Nottingham
OL,7,FInquiry, Mr Murphy described the
OL,8,Freport as "fundamentally flawed".
OL,10,FThe inquiry heard that Mr Murphy wrote
OL,11,Fthat the document is "plainly
OL,12,Fsensitive" and that "it will not be
OL,13,Fdisclosable to the defence as it
OL,14,Fdoesn't meet the CPIA (Criminal
OL,15,FProcedure and Investigations Act 1996)
OL,16,Ftest and it would plainly not be
OL,17,Fdisclosable to anyone else".
OL,26,@pD@KOUpD@`O]sD@VOUtD@JO]tD@UOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G45/57
