OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FThe survivors of the Nottingham
OL,7,Fattacks have told the inquiry that
OL,8,Fpolice failures caused "extra
OL,9,Fsuffering" for victims' families.
OL,11,FWayne Birkett, Sharon Miller and
OL,12,FMarcin Gawronski were left with life-
OL,13,Fchanging injuries after Valdo Calocane
OL,14,Fhit them with a van he'd stolen from
OL,15,FIan Coates, after he killed him.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G46/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
