CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FWayne Birkett was left with severe
OL,7,Fbrain injuries - his partner, Tracey
OL,8,FHodgson, accused Nottinghamshire
OL,9,FPolice of withholding critical
OL,10,Finformation, leaving families in
OL,11,Fprolonged anguish.
OL,13,FTracey told the Nottingham attack
OL,14,Finquiry, "It should not have needed
OL,15,Fthis inquiry for the police in
OL,16,Fparticular to tell the truth and be
OL,17,Fhonest.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G47/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37648
SC,0048
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,F"All organisations should have been
OL,7,Fopen from the beginning, and they have
OL,8,Fcaused extra suffering for the
OL,9,Ffamilies.
OL,11,F"They should have been allowed to just
OL,12,Fget on with grieving, you have
OL,13,Ftortured these families over and over
OL,14,Fagain."
OL,16,FMr Birkett was thrown into the air
OL,17,Fwhen Calocane deliberately swerved and
OL,18,Fhit him with a stolen van that he was
OL,19,Fdriving in the early hours of 13 June
OL,20,F2023 in Nottingham.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G48/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
