SC,0055
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,FElias was questioned about text
OL,7,Fmessages sent by the killer in 2020.
OL,9,FHe told the inquiry he thought an "I
OL,10,Flove you" message sent from his
OL,11,Fbrother in January of that year was a
OL,12,F"goodbye message".
OL,14,FHe added, "I guess maybe it's
OL,15,Fdifficult for people to read these
OL,16,F(text messages) now without the
OL,17,Fcontext of what happened on the 13th
OL,18,Fof June, and I completely understand
OL,19,Fthat.
OL,26,@qD@cOUrD@IO]tD@AOUtD@QO]vD@KOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G55/57
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37656
SC,0056
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781021473
OL,3,CCould Calocane have been stopped? Key
OL,4,Cmoments from the Nottingham Inquiry
OL,6,F"At this point, Valdo had never been
OL,7,Fviolent at all to anyone. He was a
OL,8,Fvery calm and peaceful person as far
OL,9,Fas I can remember."
OL,11,FThis inquiry still has some way to go.
OL,12,FThere will be concluding statements in
OL,13,FSeptember, and a full report will be
OL,14,Fpublished next year.
OL,16,FAt the start of this inquiry wanted to
OL,17,F"build a clear understanding of the
OL,18,Fevents acts and omissions" that led up
OL,19,Fto Valdo Calocane committing the
OL,20,FNottingham attacks.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G56/57
